TSWAHyperlinkBuilder

public TSWAHyperlinkBuilder(TFSTeamProjectCollection collection,
                            boolean hosted)
Creates a TSWAHyperlinkBuilder for the given TFSTeamProjectCollection.

Parameters:
collection - the collection to build links to resources in (must not be null)
hosted - true if url will be rendered as hosted content within TEE. When true, the URL contains a query parameter which instructs web access to render a page differently with knowledge that it's being hosted in another app).
